{"id":1512,"date":"2024-08-19T22:35:55","date_gmt":"2024-08-20T05:35:55","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/prowler.com\/about\/"},"modified":"2025-04-14T09:04:07","modified_gmt":"2025-04-14T16:04:07","slug":"about","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/prowler.com\/about\/","title":{"rendered":"About"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"block--hero relative pt-32 2xl:pt-28 mx-break-out px-break-out grid grid-cols-1 bg-dark min-h-[600px] lg:min-h-hero xl:min-h-screen overflow-x-hidden place-content-center pb-8\">\n                <img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1728\" height=\"1133\" src=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/about-hero-grid.svg\" class=\" object-cover absolute inset-0 object-center h-full pointer-events-none w-full z-0 ar-landscape\" alt=\"about hero grid\" \/>        <div class=\"relative z-10\">\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column flex flex-col justify-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Building a transparent, open, <mark x-data=\"{ visible: false }\" x-intersect=\"visible = true\" class=\"c-highlight\" :class=\"{ 'is-visible': visible }\"><span>secure future.<\/span><\/mark><\/h1>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"max-w-lg\">At Prowler, we recognized a significant shift in the industry towards more transparent, adaptable, and community-driven solutions. This pivot is essential in the realm of cloud security, where the landscape is rapidly evolving, and traditional black-box solutions are no longer sufficient.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons mt-24 is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-outline is-style-outline--1\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/prowler-cloud\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Explore Prowler on GitHub<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/about-hero-media-cropped.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-59\"\/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"block--ticker bg-purple mx-break-out font-mono uppercase py-4 text-white overflow-hidden relative z-10\">\n    <div\n        x-data=\"marquee(0.5)\"\n        @resize.window.debounce.100ms=\"resize\"\n        class=\"w-full inline-flex gap-x-8 flex-nowrap items-stretch animate-scrolling hover:[animation-play-state:paused]\"\n    >\n                    <span \n                class=\"whitespace-nowrap\"\n            >Get Started Easily<\/span>\n            <span class=\"text-green\">&gt;&gt;<\/span>\n                    <span \n                class=\"whitespace-nowrap\"\n            >Drive Security Innovation<\/span>\n            <span class=\"text-green\">&gt;&gt;<\/span>\n                    <span \n                class=\"whitespace-nowrap\"\n            >Stay Ahead of Threats<\/span>\n            <span class=\"text-green\">&gt;&gt;<\/span>\n            <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns min-h-challenge mb-0 is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-2 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:25%\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column flex flex-col justify-center align-center e-accent-divider is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group bg-dark py-20\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">The Challenge<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">The complexity and diversity of modern cloud environments create a unique challenge: the need to discern actionable insights from an overwhelming volume of security data. Traditional tools, with their rigid, one-size-fits-all approach, are ill-equipped to handle this complexity, leading to potential vulnerabilities, compliance issues, and slower responses to security threats.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:25%\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group e-lines-y e-break-out-to-lines\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns e-accent-divider py-32 is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-3 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column flex flex-col justify-center items-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Our Solution<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"max-w-96\">Prowler stands at the forefront of this transformation. We offer an open-source, highly configurable security platform that empowers organizations to tailor their security assessments and monitoring strategies.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column flex justify-center items-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full max-w-2xl\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/prowler-solution-chart@2x.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-929\"\/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group mb-50 mt-35\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center mb-22\">Key Features<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group c-card-grid js-tailcraft-animate\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div \n    class=\"block--icon-card bg-slate-800 rounded-2.5xl md:w-[calc(((1\/2)*100%)-((1\/2)*1.75rem))] count--1 delay-0 lg:w-[calc(((1\/3)*100%)-((2\/3)*1.75rem))] pt-5 pb-10 px-6 flex flex-col transition ease-in duration-300 translate-y-5 opacity-0\"    :class=\"{ '!translate-y-0 !opacity-100': animate }\"\n>\n            <div class=\"self-end rounded-full bg-dark flex size-25 justify-center items-center mb-10\">\n            <img decoding=\"async\" width=\"56\" height=\"54\" src=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/community-driven-icon.svg\" class=\" ar-square\" alt=\"community driven icon\" \/>        <\/div>\n                <h4 class=\"text-white text-xl\">Community-Driven<\/h4>\n                <p>Developed with and for the security community, ensuring adaptability and transparency.<\/p>\n    <\/div>\n\n\n\n<div \n    class=\"block--icon-card bg-slate-800 rounded-2.5xl md:w-[calc(((1\/2)*100%)-((1\/2)*1.75rem))] count--2 delay-250 lg:w-[calc(((1\/3)*100%)-((2\/3)*1.75rem))] pt-5 pb-10 px-6 flex flex-col transition ease-in duration-300 translate-y-5 opacity-0\"    :class=\"{ '!translate-y-0 !opacity-100': animate }\"\n>\n            <div class=\"self-end rounded-full bg-dark flex size-25 justify-center items-center mb-10\">\n            <img decoding=\"async\" width=\"53\" height=\"38\" src=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/customizable-icon.svg\" class=\" ar-landscape\" alt=\"customizable icon\" \/>        <\/div>\n                <h4 class=\"text-white text-xl\">Customizable<\/h4>\n                <p>Offers a broad range of security checks and policies, all configurable to your unique environment.<\/p>\n    <\/div>\n\n\n\n<div \n    class=\"block--icon-card bg-slate-800 rounded-2.5xl md:w-[calc(((1\/2)*100%)-((1\/2)*1.75rem))] count--3 delay-500 lg:w-[calc(((1\/3)*100%)-((2\/3)*1.75rem))] pt-5 pb-10 px-6 flex flex-col transition ease-in duration-300 translate-y-5 opacity-0\"    :class=\"{ '!translate-y-0 !opacity-100': animate }\"\n>\n            <div class=\"self-end rounded-full bg-dark flex size-25 justify-center items-center mb-10\">\n            <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"55\" height=\"55\" src=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/transparent-icon.svg\" class=\" ar-square\" alt=\"transparent icon\" \/>        <\/div>\n                <h4 class=\"text-white text-xl\">Transparent<\/h4>\n                <p>Full visibility into the logic behind each security check, empowering you to make informed decisions.<\/p>\n    <\/div>\n\n\n\n<div \n    class=\"block--icon-card bg-slate-800 rounded-2.5xl md:w-[calc(((1\/2)*100%)-((1\/2)*1.75rem))] count--4 delay-750 lg:w-[calc(((1\/3)*100%)-((2\/3)*1.75rem))] pt-5 pb-10 px-6 flex flex-col transition ease-in duration-300 translate-y-5 opacity-0\"    :class=\"{ '!translate-y-0 !opacity-100': animate }\"\n>\n            <div class=\"self-end rounded-full bg-dark flex size-25 justify-center items-center mb-10\">\n            <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"85\" height=\"84\" src=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/integrative-icon.svg\" class=\" ar-square\" alt=\"integrative icon\" \/>        <\/div>\n                <h4 class=\"text-white text-xl\">Integrative<\/h4>\n                <p>Seamlessly integrates into existing workflows with easy-to-use interfaces and visualizations.<\/p>\n    <\/div>\n\n\n\n<div \n    class=\"block--icon-card bg-slate-800 rounded-2.5xl md:w-[calc(((1\/2)*100%)-((1\/2)*1.75rem))] count--5 delay-1000 lg:w-[calc(((1\/3)*100%)-((2\/3)*1.75rem))] pt-5 pb-10 px-6 flex flex-col transition ease-in duration-300 translate-y-5 opacity-0\"    :class=\"{ '!translate-y-0 !opacity-100': animate }\"\n>\n            <div class=\"self-end rounded-full bg-dark flex size-25 justify-center items-center mb-10\">\n            <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"55\" height=\"66\" src=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/award-icon.svg\" class=\" ar-portrait\" alt=\"award icon\" \/>        <\/div>\n                <h4 class=\"text-white text-xl\">Proven and Trusted<\/h4>\n                <p>Used by leading enterprises worldwide, including parts of the Fortune 100.<\/p>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"block--simple-cta relative border-divider-dark border-y grid grid-cols-1 place-content-center min-h-screen lg:min-h-cta mx-break-out px-break-out bg-dark\">\n            <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2013\" height=\"1129\" src=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/our-vision-grid-lines-trimmed.svg\" class=\" object-cover absolute inset-0 object-center size-full pointer-events-none z-0 ar-landscape\" alt=\"our vision grid lines trimmed\" \/>        <div class=\"relative z-10 md:max-w-200 mx-auto text-center\">\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading h1\">Our <mark x-data=\"{ visible: false }\" x-intersect=\"visible = true\" class=\"c-highlight\" :class=\"{ 'is-visible': visible }\"><span>vision<\/span><\/mark><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"max-w-200\" id=\"prowler-team\">Prowler envisions a future where cloud security is driven by openness, transparency, flexibility, and accessibility. We believe in empowering security engineers to take full ownership of securing their cloud environments, with the support of a robust community.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons mt-10 gap-x-4 is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-2 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-outline is-style-outline--2\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/prowler-workspace.slack.com\/signup#\/domain-signup\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Join Slack<\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-outline is-style-outline--3\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"\/contact\/\">Get in Touch<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div id=\"team\" class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\"><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"block--post-grid e-break-out-to-lines mt-22\">\n            <h4 class=\"h2 text-center mb-24\">Leadership Team<\/h4>\n    \n    <div\n            >\n        <div \n            class=\"posts-loop flex flex-wrap md:divide-x divide-divider-dark border-divider-dark\"        >\n                                            <div class=\"w-full md:w-1\/2 lg:w-1\/4 flex justify-center\">\n   <div class=\"max-lg:px-8 lg:w-3\/4 pb-24\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" src=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Toni-de-la-Fuente-headshot-2.jpg\" class=\" rounded-full max-w-60 lg:max-w-3\/4 2xl:max-w-62 mx-auto ar-square\" alt=\"Toni de la Fuente headshot \" srcset=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Toni-de-la-Fuente-headshot-2.jpg 400w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Toni-de-la-Fuente-headshot-2-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Toni-de-la-Fuente-headshot-2-346x346.jpg 346w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" \/>        <h4 class=\"text-xl text-white mt-14\">Toni de la Fuente<\/h4>\n                    <h5>Founder and CEO<\/h5>\n                            <p class=\"my-5\">Former top security practitioner at AWS, renowned cloud security specialist, and the man who started it all with\u00a0Prowler\u00a0back in 2016.<\/p>\n         \n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.linkedin.com\/in\/toniblyx\/\">\n                <svg fill=\"none\" height=\"23\" viewBox=\"0 0 22 23\" width=\"22\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"><path d=\"m20.3125.6875c.8301 0 1.5625.73242 1.5625 1.61133v18.70117c0 .8789-.7324 1.5625-1.5625 1.5625h-18.79883c-.830076 0-1.51367-.6836-1.51367-1.5625v-18.70117c0-.87891.683594-1.61133 1.51367-1.61133zm-13.7207 18.75v-10.40039h-3.22266v10.40039zm-1.61133-11.86523c1.02539 0 1.85547-.83008 1.85547-1.85547s-.83008-1.9043-1.85547-1.9043c-1.07422 0-1.9043.87891-1.9043 1.9043s.83008 1.85547 1.9043 1.85547zm13.76953 11.86523v-5.7129c0-2.7832-.6348-4.98046-3.9062-4.98046-1.5626 0-2.6368.87891-3.0762 1.70896h-.0488v-1.41599h-3.07622v10.40039h3.22262v-5.127c0-1.3671.2442-2.6855 1.9532-2.6855 1.6601 0 1.6601 1.5625 1.6601 2.7344v5.0781z\" fill=\"#6af400\"\/><\/svg>\n            <\/a>\n           <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n                                            <div class=\"w-full md:w-1\/2 lg:w-1\/4 flex justify-center\">\n   <div class=\"max-lg:px-8 lg:w-3\/4 pb-24\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" src=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/rajiv.jpg\" class=\" rounded-full max-w-60 lg:max-w-3\/4 2xl:max-w-62 mx-auto ar-square\" alt=\"rajiv\" srcset=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/rajiv.jpg 500w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/rajiv-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/rajiv-346x346.jpg 346w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/rajiv-400x400.jpg 400w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/>        <h4 class=\"text-xl text-white mt-14\">Rajiv Taori<\/h4>\n                    <h5>Chief Operating Officer<\/h5>\n                            <p class=\"my-5\">Former AWS and SentinelOne executive. Builds and scales cloud security solutions with a focus on transparency and community-driven innovation.<\/p>\n         \n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.linkedin.com\/in\/rajivtaori\">\n                <svg fill=\"none\" height=\"23\" viewBox=\"0 0 22 23\" width=\"22\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"><path d=\"m20.3125.6875c.8301 0 1.5625.73242 1.5625 1.61133v18.70117c0 .8789-.7324 1.5625-1.5625 1.5625h-18.79883c-.830076 0-1.51367-.6836-1.51367-1.5625v-18.70117c0-.87891.683594-1.61133 1.51367-1.6